<template>
  <v-card>
		<v-navigation-drawer
			expand-on-hover
			permanent
			app
			dark
			width="230"
			mini-variant-width=70
			color="#7c5454"
		>
<!-- mdi-roman-numeral-1 -->
			<v-list>
				<v-list-item-group
					v-model="selected"
					color="pink lighten-4"
				>
				
					<v-list-item
						link
						color="pink lighten-4"
					>
						<v-list-item-icon>
							<v-icon color="#faf1ea">mdi-heart</v-icon>
						</v-list-item-icon>
						<v-list-item-title class="ml-1">Emotions</v-list-item-title>
					</v-list-item>

					<!-- Core 1000 Dataset -->
					<v-list-group
						:value="false"
						color="pink lighten-4"
						prepend-icon="mdi-numeric-1-box-multiple"
					>
						<template v-slot:activator>
							<v-list-item-title class="d-flex justify-center">Core 1000</v-list-item-title>
						</template>

						<v-list-item
								v-for="([title, icon, dataset], i) in core1000"
								:key="i"
								link
								color="pink lighten-4"
								@click="changeDataset(dataset)"
							>
								<v-list-item-icon><v-icon color="#faf1ea" v-text="icon"></v-icon></v-list-item-icon>
								<v-list-item-title v-text="title" class="ml-4"></v-list-item-title>
								<!-- {{this.selected = dataset}} -->
						</v-list-item>
					</v-list-group>

					<!-- Core 2000 Dataset -->
					<v-list-group
						:value="false"
						color="pink lighten-4"
						prepend-icon="mdi-numeric-2-box-multiple"
					>
						<template v-slot:activator>
							<v-list-item-title class="d-flex justify-center">Core 2000</v-list-item-title>
						</template>


						<v-list-item
								v-for="([title, icon, dataset], i) in core2000"
								:key="i"
								link
								color="pink lighten-4"
								@click="changeDataset(dataset)"
							>
								<v-list-item-icon><v-icon color="#faf1ea" v-text="icon"></v-icon></v-list-item-icon>
								<v-list-item-title v-text="title" class="ml-4"></v-list-item-title>
								<!-- {{this.selected = dataset}} -->
						</v-list-item>
					</v-list-group>
				</v-list-item-group>
			</v-list>
		</v-navigation-drawer>
	</v-card>
</template>

<script>
	export default {
		name: 'Sidebar',
		data () {
			return {
				core1000: [
					[ 'Set 1', 'mdi-roman-numeral-1', 'Core 1000 - 1' ],
					[ 'Set 2', 'mdi-roman-numeral-2', 'Core 1000 - 2' ],
					[ 'Set 3', 'mdi-roman-numeral-3', 'Core 1000 - 3' ],
					[ 'Set 4', 'mdi-roman-numeral-4', 'Core 1000 - 4' ],
					[ 'Set 5', 'mdi-roman-numeral-5', 'Core 1000 - 5' ],
					[ 'Set 6', 'mdi-roman-numeral-6', 'Core 1000 - 6' ],
					[ 'Set 7', 'mdi-roman-numeral-7', 'Core 1000 - 7' ],
					[ 'Set 8', 'mdi-roman-numeral-8', 'Core 1000 - 8' ],
					[ 'Set 9', 'mdi-roman-numeral-9', 'Core 1000 - 9' ],
					[ 'Set 10', 'mdi-roman-numeral-10', 'Core 1000 - 10' ],
				],
				core2000: [
					[ 'Set 1', 'mdi-roman-numeral-1', 'Core 2000 - 1' ],
					[ 'Set 2', 'mdi-roman-numeral-2', 'Core 2000 - 2' ],
					[ 'Set 3', 'mdi-roman-numeral-3', 'Core 2000 - 3' ],
					[ 'Set 4', 'mdi-roman-numeral-4', 'Core 2000 - 4' ],
					[ 'Set 5', 'mdi-roman-numeral-5', 'Core 2000 - 5' ],
					[ 'Set 6', 'mdi-roman-numeral-6', 'Core 2000 - 6' ],
					[ 'Set 7', 'mdi-roman-numeral-7', 'Core 2000 - 7' ],
					[ 'Set 8', 'mdi-roman-numeral-8', 'Core 2000 - 8' ],
					[ 'Set 9', 'mdi-roman-numeral-9', 'Core 2000 - 9' ],
					[ 'Set 10', 'mdi-roman-numeral-10', 'Core 2000 - 10' ],
				],
				selected: null,
			}
		},

		methods: {
			changeDataset: function(title) {
				this.dataset = this.datasets[this.datasets.findIndex(x => x.title == title)];
			}
		},
  }
</script>
